text: De Mora is a surname. Notable persons with that name include: * Francisco de Mora ( 1553–1610), Spanish architect * Jaime de Mora y Aragón (1925–1995), Spanish aristocrat and actor * José de Mora (1642–1724), Spanish sculptor * Juan Gómez de Mora (1586–1648), Spanish architect * Miguel Gil Moreno de Mora (1967–2000), Spanish cameraman and war correspondent * Doña Fabiola de Mora y Aragón (1928–2014), Spanish nobility, former Queen of Belgium ==See also == * Mora (disambiguation) * De la Mora
